{"tid":2054342,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【巨型貓籠】Angelababy過億豪宅曝光 貓貓住巨籠惹關注","createTime":"2020-06-07T05:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T06:38:18.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f81af7c86024376833be68c3ba97e2cfc7b3d43","tid":2054342,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"【巨型貓籠】Angelababy過億豪宅曝光 貓貓住巨籠惹關注<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3unutfIEQ4wBJIe4c4yICTn9VlE=/802x451/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5P3BNLYAJGIP7IIMSCHJA6TRFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3unutfIEQ4wBJIe4c4yICTn9VlE%3D%2F802x451%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5P3BNLYAJGIP7IIMSCHJA6TRFA.jpg&h=251f8c11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（微博圖片）<br />\n<br />\n黃曉明與楊穎（Angelababy）夫婦吸金力驚人，兩人曾經打入中國百名名人收入榜，加上投資有道，兩人都擁有不少物業。昨日，Angelababy在微博上載一張媽媽泡腳看電視的相片，並留言：「泡泡腳 奔跑吧 媽媽」。<br />\n<br />\n豪宅的巨型大廳全是落地玻璃，正正看到上海的地標「東方明珠塔」，有網民估計是黃曉明和Angelababy的愛巢，就是上海的黃金地段四季匯。Angelababy向來愛貓，在大廳內放置一個巨型貓籠，相比起，電視顯得比較細，不過有愛貓之人則指貓貓應該自由活動，不應該困在籠中，《蘋果》就此事聯絡黃曉明，他回覆表示：「籠子是牠們的家，平時牠們會在出面玩，晚上才睡在籠入面。」"},{"pid":"2a6712f94968adbffa60dee7ee035c89631d0d13","tid":2054342,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYjrYXE.png&amp;h=38cc2f66&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"674c8106eee71286c28dba742e7683fdd975699d","tid":2054342,"uid":189109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"邊有人養貓會買籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c7bd6a71b54583b36c4b8cd10f7547012d2012","tid":2054342,"uid":192929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f81af7c86024376833be68c3ba97e2cfc7b3d43","tid":2054342,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"【巨型貓籠】An